headline: Hillsborough County, Florida, Selects Tyler Technologies’ Appraisal Services to Enable Efficient and Precise Appraisals
summary: PLANO, Texas, March 27, 2025--Tyler announced today it has signed a four-year agreement with Hillsborough County, Florida, for Tyler’s Appraisal Services.
